    "font size" : 19.995,
    "text color" : "[0.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
    "content" : "4 Viewing Variables, Registers and Memory"
  }, {
    "type" : "paragraph",
    "id" : 95,
    "page number" : 5,
    "bounding box" : [ 72.0, 535.42, 538.165, 607.907 ],
    "font" : "ArialMT",
    "font size" : 10.995,
    "text color" : "[0.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
    "content" : "[p]rint​ <expression> Prints the value which the indicated ​expression​ evaluates to. expression can contain variable names (from the current scope), memory addresses, registers, and constants as its operands to various operators. It is written in C syntax, which means that in addition to arithmetic operations, you can also use casting operations and dereferencing operations."
  }, {
    "type" : "paragraph",
    "id" : 96,
    "page number" : 5,
    "bounding box" : [ 72.0, 483.817, 512.741, 517.907 ],
    "font" : "ArialMT",
    "font size" : 10.995,
    "text color" : "[0.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
    "content" : "To access the value contained in a register, replace the ​%​ character prefix with ​$​, e.g. ​$eax instead of ​%eax​."
  }, {
    "type" : "paragraph",
    "id" : 97,
    "page number" : 5,
    "bounding box" : [ 108.0, 459.921, 428.31, 485.916 ],
    "font" : "Consolas",
    "font size" : 10.995,
    "text color" : "[0.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
    "content" : "(gdb) print *(char *)($esp + $eax + my_ptr_array[13]) ‘e’"
  }, {
    "type" : "paragraph",
    "id" : 98,
    "page number" : 5,
    "bounding box" : [ 72.0, 393.817, 494.83, 442.907 ],
    "font" : "ArialMT",
    "font size" : 10.995,
    "text color" : "[0.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
    "content" : "[p]rint/x​ <expression> Prints the value which the indicated expression evaluates to as a hexadecimal number. expression​ is evaluated the same way as it is in ​print​."
  }, {
    "type" : "paragraph",
    "id" : 99,
    "page number" : 5,
    "bounding box" : [ 108.0, 369.921, 204.698, 395.916 ],
    "font" : "Consolas",
    "font size" : 10.995,
    "text color" : "[0.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
    "content" : "(gdb) p/x my_var $1 = 0x1b"
  }, {
    "type" : "paragraph",
    "id" : 100,
    "page number" : 5,
    "bounding box" : [ 72.0, 325.42, 319.787, 352.907 ],
    "font" : "ArialMT",
    "font size" : 10.995,
    "text color" : "[0.0, 0.0, 0.0]",
    "content" : "[x]/(number)(format)(unit_size)​ <address> Examines the data located in memory at address."
  }, {
    "type" : "list",
    "id" : 101,
    "level" : "7",
    "page number" : 5,
    "bounding box" : [ 90.0, 175.42, 531.023, 307.907 ],
